This is a Guessing game written in Assembly:

Once the code starts: 
1. The user is asked to input a player
2. Then the menu will appear with 5 options
3. The game is a simple game of guessing the correct number, it cost the player $1 to play the game.
4. Each correct guess grants the player $2, each incorrect guess will result in the player winning nothing.
3. You can click from the five options each having their own functions
  Option 1: Display available credits
  Option 2: Add credits 
  Option 3: Play the game
  Option 4: Display game statistics
  Option 5: Exit the game
4. Thanks for reading enjoy the game!
